snippet.title: Super Mario Land 2: 6 Golden Coins playthrough ~Longplay~
snippet.description:
This is a playthrough of Super Mario Land 2: 6 Golden Coins for the Nintendo Game Boy.

I may have more of an attachment to the first game, but 6 Golden Coins is a fun time in its own right.
